translations: n．物质化，具体化：将抽象的事物变为具体、实际存在的过程。
· The materializations of his ideas led to the creation of a successful business.
他的想法的物质化导致了一个成功的企业的创建。

sentences.sentence: But we will indeed tell you that materializations can and do occur here quite intentionally and occasional by accident.
sentences.translation: 但是我们会确切地告诉你，在这里(到另外时间点去)物质化确实可以有意和无意地进行，且有存有有过这样的体验。
